lead_paragraph: Italy's anti-establishment 5-Star Movement (M5S), which runs Rome municipality, said on Wednesday it was opposed to the city's bid to stage the 2024 summer Olympics, potentially sinking Rome's chances of victory.

headline.print_headline: Party Running Rome City Hall Denounces 2024 Olympic Bid
